IN the INTEREST OF: J.M. and C.D.; Respondents, Juvenile Officer, Respondent,
v.
D.B. (Mother), Appellant. WD 80905 Missouri Court of Appeals, Western District. ORDER FILED: April 3, 2018 Lauren Langan, Kansas City, MO, Counsel for Respondents, J.M. and C.D. Mitchell Widener, Kansas City, MO, Counsel for Respondent, Juvenile Officer. Before Division One: Thomas H. Newton, P.J., Victor C. Howard, and Karen King Mitchell, JJ.

ORDER

Per Curiam:

Mother, D.B., appeals a Jackson County Circuit Court judgment terminating her parental rights. For reasons stated in the memorandum provided to the parties, we affirm. Rule 84.16(b).
